Sentencas: Development of a reliable, easily scalable and economically feasible technology for thin-film solid electrolyte fabrication is critical for the industrial production of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Aerosol deposition of thin-film solid electrolyte membranes for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In the present work, the aerosol deposition (AD) technique has been appraised for this role.
Titulo: Aerosol deposition of thin-film solid electrolyte membranes for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The thin-film membranes of 8 mol.% yttria-stabilized zirconia (8YSZ) solid electrolyte were applied onto two-layer anode supports, with subsequent screen-printing of the composite cathodes made of (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.)95MnO3-delta (LSM) and zirconia co-stabilized with 10 mol.% scandia and 1 mol.% ceria (10Sc1CeSZ).
Titulo: Aerosol deposition of thin-film solid electrolyte membranes for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: High quality of the thin membranes produced by the aerosol deposition was confirmed by scanning electron microscopy and electrochemical measurements, including the measurements of current-voltage dependencies and impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Aerosol deposition of thin-film solid electrolyte membranes for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 850 degrees C, the anode-supported SOFCs with wet hydrogen as fuel and air as an oxidant demonstrated the open-circuit voltage above 1.04 V, whilst the power density was higher than 500 mW/cm(2).
Titulo: Aerosol deposition of thin-film solid electrolyte membranes for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells
